</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-42_ pf-text-1">First aid can be the difference between a temporary or long-lasting disability.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-44_ pf-text-1">Effective first aid training could reduce the number of workplace accidents by providing workers with knowledge and confidence to prevent the escalation of emergencies.
